Package: pdbR
Type: Package
Title: Programmatic Querying and Data Retrieval from RCSB PDB
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Neshatul", "Haque", email = c("nehaque@mcw.edu", neshathaq@gmail.com), role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides tools to query the RCSB Protein Data Bank using saved JSON queries, retrieve and parse results, and download mmCIF/PDB files. Includes retry logic, progress indicators, and metadata storage.
